title: IESTI Input Parameters
description: International Estimated Short-Term Intake parameters for acute dietary risk assessment

fields.matrixCode: Level 5 matrix code from PRIMo hierarchy
fields.unitWeightRPC: Unit weight for raw primary commodity (kg)
fields.caseIESTI: IESTI case (1, 2, or 3) determining calculation formula
fields.defaultVariabilityFactor: Default variability factor for the commodity

casesDescription.case1: Unit weight > large portion: IESTI = (U × HR × VF) / bw
casesDescription.case2: Unit weight < large portion (applies VF): IESTI = (LP × HR × VF) / bw
casesDescription.case3: Processed/blended commodities (no VF): IESTI = (LP × HR) / bw
